Copy/install the 'default' file into your nginx/sites-available/ folder
Then modify/update it to fit your server setup. 
There are 2 items that need to be updated at the bottom. 
1. Points to the location of the omniwallet www folder
2. Points to the location of the omni-redirects file in this folder
  This is the core of the API and has been abstracted out to allow easier updates in future.
